                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The average oxygen/silicon stoichiometric ratio of",
                "the target was determined as 1.24+-0.11.",
                "From this value and the measured yields at 55.degr.",
                "for the capture reactions on 160 and 28Si cr.sect.",
                "was obtained for the peak cross section at the Ep =",
                "1.65 MeV 28Si(p,gamma0) resonance, based on the cross",
                "section for the 16O(p,gamma1) reaction."
              ]
            }
